Code Design:

MainMenu
	- contains buttons/fragments? to other menus
	- Campaign, Arcade, Highscore, Options, etc

Campaign
	- contains buttons/fragments? to missions
	- list of missions to select

Arcade
	- contains buttons/fragments? to select
		- difficulty level
		- theme (background)

Highscore
	- displays list of previous highscores

Options
	- Sound options
	- character modifications

